ping is a utility to check live status of the devices on the computer network.in this a hacker or penetration tester send  ICMP
echo request to the target device and if target device is live it will reply with ICMP echo reply.Nmap is a tool that used to get useful informationon the computer network through ping
nmap is used to gather inventory information or subnet inforamtion of an organisation. New we need to know about three way hand shake too
